{"tid":1970551,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"奧運女子體操4金選手悶壞了 倒立脫褲55秒　","createTime":"2020-04-13T08:43:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-14T16:29:09.000Z","uid":49336,"like":2,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"059dde4014117fac24a57f7485c9b83b8992970a","tid":1970551,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T08:43:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/sports/20200413/ISARVQTTKQKWVWNQGDKKZJOKEM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20200413%2FISARVQTTKQKWVWNQGDKKZJOKEM%2F&d=9UZ2u2zW0crxbo%2Bu43gMWYgmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=1a4f9c98\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20200413%2FISARVQTTKQKWVWNQGDKKZJOKEM%2F&h=81e0330c\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/sports/20200413/ISARVQTTKQKWVWNQGDKKZJOKEM/</a><br />\n<br />\n生涯擁有4面奧運金牌的美國女子體操名將拜爾絲，昨於個人社交平台PO出一段高難度的倒立動作，整段影片總共錄製了55秒的時間，拜爾絲完成了脫下長褲的目標。 身高僅142公分的拜爾絲，顯然是在家閒得發慌，透過旁人協助拍攝，完成了這段影片，拜爾絲很快的先脫下了左腳長褲的褲管，但另外一隻腳卻花了3倍的時間才完成，期間拜爾絲一度重心不穩，還好最後保住身體平衡，完成這項在家裡的自我挑戰，影片PO出以來，已經累積175.9萬粉絲給予讚聲 。 <br />\n<br />\n現年23歲的美國體操黑珍珠拜爾絲，日前對外表示，自己對東京奧運延期一年舉辦感到失望，主要是擔心自己的奧運衛冕，年紀多長一歲充滿變數。(記者陳國偉)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/p/B-23sibhOHQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB-23sibhOHQ%2F&d=9UZ2u2zW0crxbo%2Bu43gMWYgmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=63455d58\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB-23sibhOHQ%2F&h=3c801249\" target=\"_blank\">www.instagram.com/p/B-23sibhOHQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zrNFX3M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzrNFX3M.jpg&h=5f064e1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BnNyyCf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBnNyyCf.jpg&h=a686615e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"78c5dd814f2c512a39e